text.tspan: NOTE: this is not a BIP39 Compatible recovery phrase

g.aria-label: Instructions: This is a paper wallet created using Vanilla. Use it as a long time secure storage of your crypto-funds. Use any of the addresses above addresses to receive, deposit funds and check the wallet balance. Use the information on the left to spend them later. Security: don't loose this paper wallet, don't ever reveal the private key, wif or the recovery phrase. Folding: fold leaving the printed side out. Fold along the dashed lines first, then dotted one. Leave only the addresses and Vanilla logo exposed. Staple or tape along che sides.
